---
title: 5. Pain C — Client-cancel propagation (PTU saver)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as the embedded assistant UI UI
    participant G as APIM Gateway<br/>buffer-response=false
    participant B as Azure OpenAI<br/>(PTU/PAYG)

    C->>G: POST /chat/completions (stream)
    G->>B: forward-request
    B-->>G: token 1
    G-->>C: token 1
    B-->>G: token 2
    Note over C: User clicks cancel<br/>(or HTTP/2 RST)
    C--xG: TCP close / RST
    G--xB: ❌ connection close<br/>propagated upstream
    Note over B: PTU/quota released<br/>immediately
    Note over C,B: ✅ No tokens billed<br/>for response no one is reading
